## Description

**Self-Destructing Updater Module**

MAGNETAR-UPDATER is a module used by MAGNETAR to deliver an update via Magisk Manager.

## Getting Started

MAGNETAR-UPDATER requires the following to function properly:

- [![MAGNETAR UNIFORM](https://img.shields.io/badge/MAGNETAR-UNIFORM%2B-289F94.svg?style=flat&logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://github.com/Kyliekyler/MAGNETAR)
- [![Magisk 23+](https://img.shields.io/badge/Magisk-23%2B-00B39B.svg?style=flat&logo=magisk)](https://github.com/topjohnwu/Magisk) [![KernelSU 10647+](https://img.shields.io/badge/KernelSU-10647%2B-1E110D.svg?style=flat&logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://github.com/tiann/KernelSU)

Only MAGNETAR would be able to utilize this automatically. This updater module should not be flashed on its own.
